#description
  h2 What is Z-Tooltips ?
  
  p 
    | Z-Tooltips is the easyest and most lightweight way to provide beautiful tooltips 
    | on your web pages.

  p 
    | You'll just have to write your tooltip's content in a 
    span.inline-code data-ztooltips
    | attribut instead of the usual 
    span.inline-code title 
    | attribute.

  .grid
    .grid-2.center
      .box
        a(href="https://github.com/benavern/z-tooltips", data-ztooltips="View this project on Github").btn.z-tooltips-top 
          span.entypo-github 
          | github
      
    .grid-2.center
      .box
        a(href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/z-tooltips", data-ztooltips="View this project on npm").btn 
          span.entypo-rocket 
          | npm
  
